<br>
She nodded to Nike as she felt her hand on her shoulder and gently patted the hand that was placed there shortly before moving. She glanced over to her step-mother and saw the curious look in her eyes.<br>
<br>
Athena gave a smirk knowing that Eris had no where near the power that Athena held. No where near.<br>
<br>
She folded her arms with a smirk being satisified with her thoughts before Eris tried to suck up to Zeus. Then she had, had it.<br>
<br>
Athena stood looking to Eris, the trouble maker.<br>
